title: 10/30/2020 - Best of The Herd

description:
-The Ravens and Steelers dominance illustrate how bad the Browns truly are

-Thursday night was a bad night for the Falcons

-The NFL can be broken down into three groups of teams

-Dallas Cowboys fans should want to get embarrassed by the Eagles

-Some people get what the Patriots are doing more than the media does


Guest: Matthew McConaughey, Award winning Actor
